<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Samsung Galaxy S26 </title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: Times New Roman, serif;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }
    
    .navbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 15px 40px;
      background-color: #111;
      color: white;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: #00adb5;
    }

    .product {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 60px;
      gap: 50px;
      background-color: white;
    }

    .product img {
      width: 320px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }

    .product-details {
      max-width: 450px;
    }

    .product-details h2 {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .product-details p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .product-details button {
      padding: 12px 25px;
      border: none;
      background-color: #00adb5;
      color: white;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .product-details button:hover {
      background-color: #008c94;
    }

    .features {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
      padding: 60px;
    }

    .card {
      background-color: white;
      padding: 25px;
      width: 260px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .card p {
      color: #666;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .product {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .features {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="navbar">
    <h1>Samsung</h1>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#">Home</a>
      <a href="#">Features</a>
      <a href="#">Buy</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="product">
    <img src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71aodJE5MfL._AC_UF1000,1000_QL80_.jpg" alt="Samsung S26">
    <div class="product-details">
      <h2>Samsung Galaxy S26</h2>
      <p>The Samsung Galaxy S26 features a 6.3-inch display, the high-performance Snapdragon 8 Elite Gen 5 (or Exynos 2600) chipset, and advanced "Agentic AI" for proactive task management. It maintains a sleek, professional aesthetic with a 50MP triple-camera system and improved low-light video capabilities.</p>
      <button>Buy Now</button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Agentic AI Integration</h3>
      <p>The S26 features One UI 8.5 with proactive "Agentic AI" that can solve complex engineering equations and automate multi-step tasks across your apps.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Professional Triple Camera</h3>
      <p>The phone has a 50MP main camera alongside dedicated wide-angle and zoom lenses, allowing you to take sharp, high-quality photos in almost any lighting condition.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Long Battery</h3>
      <p>It is equipped with a 4,300 mAh battery and smarter power management, designed to easily last a full day of heavy use on a single charge.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
